snippet.title: Ramayana The Introduction Teaser REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Ramayana The Introduction Teaser Review By Deeksha Sharma. Namit Malhotra's Ramayana Directed by Nitesh Tiwari Presents Ranbir Kapoor in The IMMORTAL story of Rama v/s Ravana- Full of History Detailing, Top Quality Special Effects by DNEG & Powerful yet Unique Background Music Created by Hans Zimmer & AR Rahman Ramayana Promises the Biggest Cinema Adventure ever produced in Indian Film Industry. Starring Ranbir Kapoor as Rama, Yash as Ravana, Sai Pallavi as Sita, Ravie Dubey as Lakshman & Sunny Deol as Hanuman - Ramayana Part 1 is set for Diwali 2026 release date. Ramayana The Introduction Teaser Trailer Review Reaction & full Movie Expectations would be shared in this Video. We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

Parwarish Episode 25 | Digitally Presented by Surf Excel , Vince Care, Mothercare &  VGOTEL | Aina Asif | Samar Jafri | Reham Rafiq | 1st JULY 2025 | ARY Digital Drama 

PARWARISH â€“ The most-watched Pakistani drama of the season, Parwarish is a gripping tale of generational conflict, where love becomes control and independence feels like rebellion. As parents hold tight to cultural traditions and children chase dreams of freedom, misunderstandings shake the very foundation of the family. Itâ€™s a powerful reflection of the emotional battles playing out in households across Pakistan today.


Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir:
Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his fatherâ€™s disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the dramaâ€™s central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Beautiful and self-assured, she aspires to become a doctorâ€”a path her family supports only conditionally. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in todayâ€™s society.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Tag Awara Ke (Official Video) Amanraj Gill, Shivani Yadav, Shiva Choudhary | New Haryanvi Song 2024

Nav Haryanvi Presenting "Tag Awara Ke (Official Video)" a New Haryanvi Songs Haryanavi 2024. Sung by Amanraj Gill and Shiva Choudhary. Starring with Shivani Yadav. Lyrics are Penned by Amanraj Gill. Music given by Amanraj Gill. Music Label by Nupur Audio.

Lyrics : 
Oh thare laagale kyon sharey aam ye tag awara ke
Kade pahada mein kade akhada mein ravein dere yaaran ke

Kade pahada mein kade akhada mein ravein dere yaaran ke
Thare 2 number ke kaam nire taqleefaan aale rey


Gaadi ke number pe satte 
Raakhe dass dass gela patthey
Khele zindagi gele satte
Naa kaam shareefaan aale re

Gaadi mein karwa ke hooter
Rakhu gel bithake shooter
Maara raah rokan je chahiye
Jaiye sey chhati mein gaadey rey

Kyun itne masle rakhey
Aatma rakhey kashti mein
Jo khatkhyaa jaan drishti mein
Woh paaya nahi shrishti mein


Jo khatkhyaa jaan drishti mein
Woh paaya nahi shrishti mein
Maare khoon ubaaley taate
Lade jawani aale jaatey

Tadke mare sapate
Chhorey paale chhaley rey

Gaadi ke number pe satte 
Raakhe dass dass gela patthey
Khele zindagi gele satte
Naa kaam shareefaan aale re

Gaadi mein karwa ke hooter
Rakhu gel bithake shooter
Maara raah rokan je chahiye
Jaiye sey chhati mein gaadey rey

Chaale saare ye theke aa tola banau
Kara deve hain saare callan pe kaam
Maahri nyaari hain line ji me laagde na jaam
Kyon leve bhadak le baba ka naam

Rupiya naa rakhte hum locker mein madam
Duniyaa ne mane thokkar pe madam
Hawa mein rehna toh banta hain zindagi mein
Chhattaan pe utre jinke helicopter hain madam

Positive chhora konya tootti smile
Easy schedule rave kaan pe mobile
Maare kharchein ne charche ne parche ne dekh
Khule lokkaan de munh band ho jaa se thaa hi

Tu ravey udatta note yaari mein
Tanne jodyaa ke
Kothiyan car-aan wala dharti ae
Vaas crore-aan ki

Kothiyan car-aan aale dharti ae
Vaas crore-aan ki
Note-aan ki bhar ri almaari
Kade pajero kade safari

Buddhi amne teri anaari
Kadi naa tenta taale rey

snippet.title: Charity or Showbiz? | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
In this short video, we reflect on a growing concern within our churches,  are we truly giving from the heart, or are we more concerned about our name being announced in public? Too often, people give generously to the church just to gain recognition, while neglecting genuine needs like community development or council initiatives that benefit everyone.

Letâ€™s pause and ask ourselves: Is our giving rooted in love, faith, and responsibility â€” or is it driven by pride and empty tradition? True giving is quiet, sincere, and purposeful.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

How to make tikhat mitachya purya | Ashadh Special Tikhat purya Recipe | How to make Ashadh special kapanya dhapate recipe
For the paste:To prepare the paste, take garlic, green chilies, cumin seeds, and carom seeds in a mixer jar and grind them to a paste.
To knead the puri dough:Now in a large mixing bowl, add wheat flour, sorghum flour, gram flour, and salt. Mix everything well.Heat the oil taken for shortening until it's very hot, and pour it over the flour mixture. First mix using a spoon, then rub it into the flour with your hands thoroughly.Now add the prepared paste, turmeric, white sesame seeds, chopped coriander, and dried fenugreek leaves. Mix well and knead into a stiff dough by adding a little water at a time.After kneading, apply a little oil on the dough and cover it for 10 minutes.
While rolling the puris:Roll one large roti (flatbread) and cut puris using a glass or tumbler, or roll small individual puris and keep ready for frying.
Frying the puris:Heat oil on medium flame. Once the oil is hot, add a few puris at a time (as many as the pan can hold). After adding, reduce the flame to medium and fry the puris well on both sides until crisp and golden.
Note:These puris are traditionally made during the month of Ashadha and served with raw mango pieces. Once cooled, they can be stored in an airtight container and will stay fresh for up to a month. They are a great option for travel or picnics.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi

Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi

snippet.title: The Coldest Village on Earth (10 minutes outside = Death) -71Â°C, -96Â°F
snippet.description:
Use the coupon code RUHI29 to buy the MyHeritage DNA kit for only $29/â‚¬29/Â£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH or start your family tree with a 14-day free trial.

Here is my friend's video:
Journey to the World's Coldest Village: Oymyakon at -71Â°C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Don't forget to check out "The Ulengovs" channel: https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Thanks to MyHeritage for sponsoring this video.

Imagine a village where temperatures drop as low as -71Â°C, -96Â°F. Here, spending just a few extra minutes outside can lead to frostbite, the loss of a limb, or even end of life.

Iâ€™m in the coldest inhabited place on Earth, at the coldest time of the year. This is Oymyakon. Just to stay alive, Iâ€™m wearing more than 20 layers of clothing, weighing nearly 14 kilos. Stepping outside from a warm 30Â°C home means facing a temperature drop of over 100 degrees. Thatâ€™s why Iâ€™m also wearing gloves, boots, pants, and a coat, all made from reindeer fur. And even thatâ€™s not enough. And now, Iâ€™m about to show you what life is like when simply going outside becomes a battle for survival.

The cold doesn't just affect people and wild animals. It stops everything from functioning.  Phones donâ€™t work properly and often shut down. Cars left outside freeze in just a few hours. Since the ground is always frozen, no fruits or vegetables can grow here.

We boarded a plane in Moscow, flying east for seven hours to Yakutsk. From there, we covered an 18 hour, 900 kilometer road trip. When we stepped out of the car, it felt like we were on another planet. The hairs in our nose were frozen, and we felt them prick with every breath. The dry air makes us cough uncontrollably.  

Oymyakon is home to around 800 people, spread across 1.5 square kilometers. Seeing anyone else outside is almost impossible, the village feels like it has been abandoned.

Our team that worked on this project â–º https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vDYIkyfFR1fayrUZOsA80xEN3X-nYhU003F1FewGCy8/edit?usp=sharing

Visiting the World's Hottest Place (70Â°C, 159Â°F) LUT DESERT â–º https://youtu.be/NhyDkHaUC8U
Visiting the Worldâ€™s Most DaĞ¿geĞ³ous Road: â€œKarakoram Dâ„®ath Roadâ€ (There are casuaItiâ„®s!) â–º https://youtu.be/FryCzL17YRs
Visiting the MOST AIR POLLUTED CITY in the World (Dust Hell) â–º https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Visiting the COLDEST CITY in the World (-71Â°C, -96Â°F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA â–º https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM
8 Crazy Experiments at -55Â°C, -67Â°F (The coldest city in the World: Yakutsk) â–º https://youtu.be/ExoOL2lwlWE
World's Poorest Country "Burundi" (I canâ€™t forget the things I saw) â–º https://youtu.be/n0gFsHf9cIw

en.title: The Coldest Village on Earth (10 minutes outside = Death) -71Â°C, -96Â°F
en.description:
Use the coupon code RUHI29 to buy the MyHeritage DNA kit for only $29/â‚¬29/Â£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH or start your family tree with a 14-day free trial.

Here is my friend's video:
Journey to the World's Coldest Village: Oymyakon at -71Â°C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Don't forget to check out "The Ulengovs" channel: https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Thanks to MyHeritage for sponsoring this video.

Imagine a village where temperatures drop as low as -71Â°C, -96Â°F. Here, spending just a few extra minutes outside can lead to frostbite, the loss of a limb, or even end of life.

Iâ€™m in the coldest inhabited place on Earth, at the coldest time of the year. This is Oymyakon. Just to stay alive, Iâ€™m wearing more than 20 layers of clothing, weighing nearly 14 kilos. Stepping outside from a warm 30Â°C home means facing a temperature drop of over 100 degrees. Thatâ€™s why Iâ€™m also wearing gloves, boots, pants, and a coat, all made from reindeer fur. And even thatâ€™s not enough. And now, Iâ€™m about to show you what life is like when simply going outside becomes a battle for survival.

The cold doesn't just affect people and wild animals. It stops everything from functioning.  Phones donâ€™t work properly and often shut down. Cars left outside freeze in just a few hours. Since the ground is always frozen, no fruits or vegetables can grow here.

We boarded a plane in Moscow, flying east for seven hours to Yakutsk. From there, we covered an 18 hour, 900 kilometer road trip. When we stepped out of the car, it felt like we were on another planet. The hairs in our nose were frozen, and we felt them prick with every breath. The dry air makes us cough uncontrollably.  

Oymyakon is home to around 800 people, spread across 1.5 square kilometers. Seeing anyone else outside is almost impossible, the village feels like it has been abandoned.

Immaginate un villaggio dove le temperature scendono fino a -71 Â°C, -96 Â°F. Qui, trascorrere solo pochi minuti in piÃ¹ all'aperto puÃ² portare a congelamenti, alla perdita di un arto o persino alla fine della vita.

Mi trovo nel luogo abitato piÃ¹ freddo della Terra, nel periodo piÃ¹ freddo dell'anno. Questa Ã¨ Oymyakon. Solo per sopravvivere, indosso piÃ¹ di 20 strati di vestiti, per un peso di quasi 14 chili. Uscire da una casa calda a 30 Â°C significa affrontare un calo di temperatura di oltre 38 gradi. Ecco perchÃ© indosso anche guanti, stivali, pantaloni e un cappotto, tutti di pelliccia di renna. E anche questo non basta. E ora sto per mostrarvi com'Ã¨ la vita quando semplicemente uscire diventa una lotta per la sopravvivenza.

Il freddo non colpisce solo le persone e gli animali selvatici. Impedisce a tutto di funzionare. I telefoni non funzionano correttamente e spesso si spengono. Le auto lasciate fuori si congelano in poche ore. Dato che il terreno Ã¨ sempre ghiacciato, qui non cresce nÃ© frutta nÃ© verdura.

Quando siamo scesi dall'auto, ci siamo sentiti come su un altro pianeta. I peli del naso erano congelati e li sentivamo pungere a ogni respiro. L'aria secca ci fa tossire in modo incontrollabile.

Oymyakon ospita circa 800 persone, distribuite su 1,5 chilometri quadrati. Vedere qualcun altro all'esterno Ã¨ quasi impossibile, il villaggio sembra abbandonato.

id.title: Desa Terdingin di Dunia (10 Menit di Luar = Kematian) -71Â°C
id.description:
Gunakan kode kupon RUHI29 untuk membeli kit DNA MyHeritage hanya seharga $29/â‚¬29/Â£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH atau mulai silsilah keluarga Anda dengan uji coba gratis selama 14 hari.
Berikut adalah video teman saya:
Perjalanan ke Desa Terdingin di Dunia: Oymyakon pada suhu -71Â°C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Jangan lupa untuk menonton saluran "The Ulengovs": https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Bayangkan sebuah desa yang suhunya turun hingga -71Â°C, -96Â°F. Di sini, menghabiskan beberapa menit di luar ruangan saja dapat menyebabkan radang dingin, kehilangan anggota tubuh, atau bahkan akhir hidup.

Saya berada di tempat berpenghuni terdingin di Bumi, pada waktu terdingin dalam setahun. Ini adalah Oymyakon. Agar tetap hidup, saya mengenakan lebih dari 20 lapis pakaian, yang beratnya hampir 14 kilogram. Melangkah keluar dari rumah yang hangat bersuhu 30Â°C berarti menghadapi penurunan suhu lebih dari 100 derajat. Itu sebabnya saya juga mengenakan sarung tangan, sepatu bot, celana, dan mantel, yang semuanya terbuat dari bulu rusa kutub. Itu pun belum cukup. Dan sekarang, saya akan menunjukkan kepada Anda seperti apa kehidupan saat sekadar keluar rumah menjadi pertempuran untuk bertahan hidup.

Cuaca dingin tidak hanya memengaruhi manusia dan hewan liar. Cuaca dingin menghentikan semua fungsi. Ponsel tidak berfungsi dengan baik dan sering mati. Mobil yang ditinggal di luar membeku hanya dalam beberapa jam. Karena tanah selalu beku, tidak ada buah atau sayuran yang dapat tumbuh di sini.

Kami naik pesawat di Moskow, terbang ke timur selama tujuh jam menuju Yakutsk. Dari sana, kami menempuh perjalanan darat selama 18 jam, sejauh 900 kilometer. Saat kami keluar dari mobil, rasanya seperti berada di planet lain. Bulu hidung kami membeku, dan kami merasakannya menusuk setiap kali bernapas. Udara kering membuat kami batuk-batuk tak terkendali.

Oymyakon adalah rumah bagi sekitar 800 orang, tersebar di wilayah seluas 1,5 kilometer persegi. Hampir mustahil untuk melihat orang lain di luar, desa itu terasa seperti telah ditinggalkan.

Tim kami yang mengerjakan proyek ini: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OOPAk_iEyW2ykhtBRo4g4X3kFq44Uny9H50L970WFoo/edit?usp=sharing

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Dayan Aflevering 38 - [Engelse ondertiteling] - Mehwish Hayat - Ahsan Khan - Hira Mani - 1 juli 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Dayan is een aangrijpend verhaal over een meisje dat vecht voor gerechtigheid na een reeks onrechtvaardigheden te hebben moeten doorstaan. Het volgt Nihaal, een jonge vrouw wiens leven wordt verwoest door een tragische wending. De gebeurtenissen die volgen, schudden Nihaal tot in haar diepste wezen en veranderen haar persoonlijkheid drastisch. Dit zet Nihaal ertoe aan om op reis te gaan om degenen die verantwoordelijk zijn voor haar leven voor de rechter te brengen.

Kan Nihaal de gerechtigheid krijgen die ze verdient? Is Nihaal sterk genoeg om degenen die haar onrecht hebben aangedaan te verslaan? Kan Nihaal alles aan wat het leven haar brengt?

Dayan Episode 38 - [Eng Sub] - Mehwish Hayat - Ahsan Khan - Hira Mani - 1 Juli 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Dayan adalah kisah mencekam tentang seorang gadis yang memperjuangkan keadilan setelah mengalami serangkaian ketidakadilan. Kisah ini mengikuti Nihaal, seorang wanita muda yang hidupnya hancur oleh serangkaian peristiwa tragis. Peristiwa yang terjadi kemudian mengguncang Nihaal hingga ke inti dirinya, mengubah kepribadiannya secara drastis. Dapatkah Nihaal mendapatkan keadilan yang layak diterimanya? Apakah Nihaal cukup kuat untuk mengalahkan orang-orang yang telah berbuat salah padanya? Dapatkah Nihaal menghadapi semua yang terjadi dalam hidupnya?

Humraaz Digitally Presented by Skin White Rice Milk Facewash - Happilac Paints & Meclay London Shampoo

Humraaz is a unique tale of love, fate, and redemption, exploring the profound impact of a single tragic event on the lives of three individuals named Sara, Ahmer, and Saim. Sara is a vibrant and free-spirited young woman in a relationship with Ahmer. Meanwhile, Saim, a young and charming man, lives a life entirely separate from Sara and Ahmer. However, their paths cross dramatically when an unexpected tragedy occurs, deeply impacting Saim's life.

With all the evidence pointing toward her, suspicion quickly falls on Sara but she firmly denies any wrongdoing. Yet, Saim is convinced of her guilt and is determined to seek justice. As fate brings Sara, Ahmer, and Saim together in unforeseen ways, they must confront difficult truths, navigate confusion, and unravel the mystery behind the tragedy.

Is Sara truly the reason behind it all? Can Ahmer help clear Saraâ€™s name? Will Ahmer choose to trust Sara or walk away? Is Sara truly loyal to Ahmer? Will Saim uncover the truth about Saraâ€™s involvement? And will the mystery of the real culprit finally be solved?

Humraaz adalah kisah unik tentang cinta, takdir, dan penebusan, mengeksplorasi dampak mendalam dari satu peristiwa tragis pada kehidupan tiga individu bernama Sara, Ahmer, dan Saim. Sara adalah wanita muda yang bersemangat dan berjiwa bebas yang menjalin hubungan dengan Ahmer. Sementara itu, Saim, seorang pria muda yang menawan, menjalani hidup yang sepenuhnya terpisah dari Sara dan Ahmer. Namun, jalan hidup mereka bertemu secara dramatis ketika sebuah tragedi tak terduga terjadi, yang berdampak besar pada kehidupan Saim.

Dengan semua bukti yang mengarah padanya, kecurigaan segera jatuh pada Sara tetapi dia dengan tegas menyangkal segala kesalahan. Namun, Saim yakin akan kesalahannya dan bertekad untuk mencari keadilan. Saat takdir mempertemukan Sara, Ahmer, dan Saim dengan cara yang tak terduga, mereka harus menghadapi kebenaran yang sulit, mengatasi kebingungan, dan mengungkap misteri di balik tragedi tersebut.

Apakah Sara benar-benar alasan di balik semuanya? Bisakah Ahmer membantu membersihkan nama Sara? Akankah Ahmer memilih untuk mempercayai Sara atau menjauh? Apakah Sara benar-benar setia kepada Ahmer? Akankah Saim mengungkap kebenaran tentang keterlibatan Sara? Dan apakah misteri pelaku sebenarnya akhirnya akan terpecahkan?

Some love stories aren't just written in heartsâ€”they're carved through pain, sacrifice, and fire. Enter the world of Sher, where two soulsâ€”Sher Zaman and Fajarâ€”dare to love beyond the lines drawn by generations of hate.

Danish Taimoor breathes life into Sher Zaman, a man raised with command in his veinsâ€”fierce, proud, and built to lead.
Sarah Khan shines as Fajar, a gentle heart swept into the storm of a family feud, trying to hold on to love and light in a world clouded by old grudges.

Their paths were never meant to cross. But loveâ€¦ had other plans.

Sher is a gripping Pakistani drama packed with raw emotions, intense rivalries, and deep-rooted traditions.
From kidnappings and secret alliances to broken promises and forbidden love, every episode leaves you wanting more.
Featuring a stellar cast and top-tier storytelling from the makers of iconic drama hits.

snippet.title: The Running Man | Official Trailer (2025 Movie) - Edgar Wright, Glen Powell
snippet.description:
Millions Hunt. One Runs. Everyone Watches. Watch the Official Trailer for The #RunningManMovie â€“ Only in theatres November 7

â€‹In a near-future society, The Running Man is the top-rated show on televisionâ€”a deadly competition where contestants, known as Runners, must survive 30 days while being hunted by professional assassins, with every move broadcast to a bloodthirsty public and each day bringing a greater cash reward. Desperate to save his sick daughter, working-class Ben Richards (Glen Powell) is convinced by the showâ€™s charming but ruthless producer, Dan Killian (Josh Brolin), to enter the game as a last resort. But Benâ€™s defiance, instincts, and grit turn him into an unexpected fan favoriteâ€”and a threat to the entire system. As ratings skyrocket, so does the danger, and Ben must outwit not just the Hunters, but a nation addicted to watching him fall.

snippet.description:
Bina Bread ke Crispy Bread Roll #breadroll â€“ Ab banayein super tasty Bread Roll Recipe bina bread ke bhi, woh bhi full crispy aur perfect tea time snack ke saath! Yeh Bread Roll Recipe thodi hatke hai, jisme bread nahi lekin texture aur crunch bilkul same milta hai. Aloo stuffing, crisp outer layer aur street-style swad ke saath yeh Bina Bread ke Bread Roll sabko surprise karega. Agar aap bread nahi use karna chahte, toh yeh Bread Roll Recipe aapke liye best hai.

Preparation time - 20 minutes
Serving - 8

Ingredients : 
Boiled Potato - 4 pcs
Red Chilli Powder - 1 tsp
Salt as per Taste
Cumin
Chaat Masala - 1 tsp
Chopped Green Chilli - 3 Pcs
Chopped Ginger - 1 inch
Chopped Onion - 1 pcs (medium size)
Chopped Coriander Leaves
Schezwan Sauce - 1 tsp
Poha - 2  cup
Gram Flour - 1/2 cup (5 tbsp)
Oil

Tanjiro Kamado â€“ a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon.

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corpsâ€™ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. snippet.title: NEW MOB AND GEAR IN THE NEXT GAME DROP!
snippet.description:
Clink-clonk! Whatâ€™s that sound, you ask? Itâ€™s a new friend who will hang around your base and keep your chests tidy! Get reacquainted with the copper golem, brought back from a previous mob vote to organize your inventory and delight you with its overwhelming cuteness. 

Join Agnes Larsson (inside an actual copper mine!), Matthew Clohessy, and Eric Grimsborn as they give us the scoop on making the copper golem and its copper chest as well as the copper gear! Why are they SO excited about copper tools? And did Agnes remember to place torches as she ventured into the mine? Keep watching and find out! 

Test the copper golem, chest, and gear and send us your feedback at bugs.mojang.com!

Go to www.falugruva.se to learn more about the mine Agnes visited!

* Vibrant Visuals graphics upgrade is currently only available for compatible Minecraft: Bedrock Edition devices. Coming in the future to Java Edition.

Note: we accidentally featured a mis-colored glowberry in this Dev Diary. Whoops! Though we have been known to sneak secrets into our videos, this is an actual mistake and doesn't hint at anything. We are working on game drops packed with new features, but re-colored glowberries aren't one of them. Apologies to fans of cave fruit!

Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to.
